==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unexpected
<hw>Un`ex*pect"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not expected;
coming without warning; sudden.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un`ex*pect"ed*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un`ex*pect"ed*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

